'''亚洲公路42号线'''（{{lang-en|'''Asian Highway 42'''}}）编号{{Asian Highway nopic|42}}，是[[亞洲公路網|亞洲公路網]]系統中的一條全长{{convert|3754|km}}公路，起点在[[中国|中国]][[兰州|兰州]]{{Asian Highway nopic|5}}<ref>Economic and Social Commission for Asia and the Pacific, [http://www.unescap.org/ttdw/Publications/TIS_pubs/pub_2303/Full%20version.pdf 2003 Asian Highway Handbook] {{Wayback|url=http://www.unescap.org/ttdw/Publications/TIS_pubs/pub_2303/Full%20version.pdf |date=20120414184019 }}, 2003, page 32</ref>，终点在位于[[印度|印度]][[巴尔希|巴尔希]]{{Asian Highway nopic|1}}。<ref>Economic and Social Commission for Asia and the Pacific, [http://www.unescap.org/ttdw/Publications/TIS_pubs/pub_2303/Full%20version.pdf 2003 Asian Highway Handbook] {{Wayback|url=http://www.unescap.org/ttdw/Publications/TIS_pubs/pub_2303/Full%20version.pdf |date=20120414184019 }}, 2003, page 41</ref>

AH42途径[[中国|中国]]、[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]<ref>Economic and Social Commission for Asia and the Pacific, [http://www.unescap.org/ttdw/Publications/TIS_pubs/pub_2303/Full%20version.pdf 2003 Asian Highway Handbook] {{Wayback|url=http://www.unescap.org/ttdw/Publications/TIS_pubs/pub_2303/Full%20version.pdf |date=20120414184019 }}, 2003, page 78</ref>和[[印度|印度]]，是最靠近[[珠穆朗玛峰|珠穆朗玛峰]]的亚洲公路。

